--- Switchblade ---

Switchblade shakes his head, when he hears the explosion of anti-
matter. <<Another one bites the dust,>> he thinks... <<I wonder if 
there will be enough of Fireblade to pick up... At least he nailed the 
b**** good...>> he smiles cruelly.


On 14 May 2001, at 5:41, gunthers8@... wrote:

> ::FireBlade::
> FireBlade knowing SwitchBlades intentions let the acid hit his arm. In
> his state of rage he didn't notice.Not knowing if that acid affected
> IR's tail he threw his sword end over end at IR and grabbed his back
> using his strength to fight the tail off.  He grabbed the explosive
> and cocked his wrist sticking it on IR's tail. Beeping started to emit
> and a second or two....ka boom...
